<ul>
  <li>The company recently concluded large investment in IT systems overhaul</li>
  <li>A lack of an IT cost control culture and business case processes created redundant and increasing expenditures</li>
  <li>Vendor consolidations and software re-sale agreements hampered visibility into the “cost of application” calculation</li>
  <li>Property ownership groups required more detailed explanation for the IT component of franchisee charges and needed transparency</li>
  <li>Convoluted and non-standard invoice approval processes furthered cost uncertainty and tracking issues</li>
